overview: Starring Coco Winchester (Blonde 1), 'SleepWalk' is a surrealist film based around girlhood struggles, identity and detachment from reality. The short film follows the protagonist through her daily routine as a disordered teenage girl which is interrupted by a faceless individual. This film is completely up to the viewers interpretation based on their own struggles.
tagline: mental health, detachment, surrealism, interpretive, my year of rest and relaxation.
title: SleepWalk
